Pragya Nursery — live ordering platform


A real ordering platform for my father’s plant nursery in Greater Noida. Vercel website, Render API, Capacitor Android app, Paytm payments, geofenced delivery within 15 km, persistent order storage, CI-deployed on every push to master. Live customers, real revenue.




