&lt;h1 class="about-name"&gt;Prerna Tyagi&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p class="about-tagline"&gt;AI/ML engineer who &lt;strong&gt;ships&lt;/strong&gt;. Currently turning a model-focused data-science background into applied AI engineering for production systems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class="about-bio"&gt;Self-taught the production half of the stack — APIs, deployment, observability, evals — by building a real e-commerce platform for my father's plant nursery and writing a long-form series implementing the building blocks of modern AI from scratch.&lt;/p&gt;

